{"tid":1587302,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民主確保唔到經濟繁榮，但係確保制衡到警權","createTime":"2019-09-22T10:46:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T17:06:44.000Z","uid":33799,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3158b58a5afda1453e471e0d0c078f2802217b0e","tid":1587302,"uid":33799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T10:46:53.000Z","msg":"一個民主政府既授權係黎自人民，唔係好似軍政府咁依靠武力鎮壓。今時今日香港既情況就係話俾香港人知民主既可貴，而香港警察必然係民主既敵人，因為佢地一定會反對任何真正既民主政制改革，以避免任何不利佢地濫權既限制。<br />\n<br />\n所以所有抗爭者（由其是左膠）必須有覺悟，將來既仗唔好再對警察有任何幻想，唔好再用佢地都俾香港政府利用開脫，否則只會害死同路人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaa088223b28d3ae47537f877fff11128270c134","tid":1587302,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T10:47:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1566f01787ba08d082fae45ad2aa4c9494aaebd3","tid":1587302,"uid":33799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T17:06:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"71112aff22e3ce70273061259e6337c5e2dfd46f","tid":1587302,"uid":33799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T17:06:44.000Z","msg":"大家要知自己爭取緊啲咩"}]}